This paper is likely to belong to the Graphics (cs.GR) and Computer Vision (cs.CV) categories as it deals with material modeling and rendering. The use of convolutional neural networks also suggests that it could belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) categories. Finally, the mention of denoising and neural rendering techniques suggests that it could also belong to the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) category.
